2.2 Administrator
Operations Manager Role:

✅ Create, edit, delete ALL monitors
✅ Configure alerts for all monitors
✅ View all reports and analytics
✅ Receive email alerts
❌ Cannot manage users 
❌ Cannot access system configuration


2.3 Manager
Team Lead Role:

✅ Create and manage their own monitors
✅ Assign their monitors to Viewers
✅ Configure alerts for their monitors
✅ View reports for their monitors only,export reports
✅ Receive email alerts for their monitors
❌ Cannot access other managers' monitors
❌ Cannot manage users but add new Viewer account 
❌ Cannot access system settings


2.4 Viewer
Read-Only Observer:

✅ View monitors assigned to them
✅ View status and statistics (read-only)
✅ View incident history (read-only)
❌ Cannot create or edit monitors
❌ Cannot receive email alerts
❌ Cannot export reports


4. User Management Features (Super Admin Only)
4.1 User List View

View all users with name, email, role, status
Search by name or email
Filter by role (Admin, Manager, Viewer)
Filter by status (Active, Inactive)
Sort by name, role, or last login

4.2 Create User
Required Fields:

Full name
Email address
Role (Admin, Manager, Viewer)
Initial password

Actions After Creation:

Send welcome email with credentials
Force password change on first login
Account is Active by default

4.3 Edit User
Editable:

Name, email, role, status
Reset password
Activate/Deactivate account

View:

Login history
Created monitors count
Assigned monitors

4.4 Delete User
Confirmation Required:

Show user details
Choose what happens to their monitors:

Transfer to another user
Mark as unassigned
Delete monitors



